fields.description: Indicates the result of the CA policy that was triggered. Possible values are: success, failure, notApplied (policy isn't applied because policy conditions weren't met), notEnabled (This is due to the policy in a disabled state), unknown, unknownFutureValue, reportOnlySuccess, reportOnlyFailure, reportOnlyNotApplied, reportOnlyInterrupted. You must use the Prefer: include-unknown-enum-members request header to get the following values in this evolvable enum: reportOnlySuccess, reportOnlyFailure, reportOnlyNotApplied, reportOnlyInterrupted.
